Muriel Evans https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Muriel_Evans 0 Muriel Evans (born Muriel Adele Evanson, July 20, 1910 – October 26, 2000) was an American film actress. She is best known for her many appearances in popular westerns of the 1930s for which she won a Golden Boot Award.
